deck: K.H. Lee is a visionary who works tirelessly on revitalizing Korea's homegrown comic book industry by helping to promote up and coming talent. He is the driving force behind Bluewolf (bluewolf.me) - a great publisher of Korean language stories ranging from fairy tales to horror. Without him, many young Korean talents would have given up on comic books a long time ago.
name: K.H. Lee
